"uid":135517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T01:57:49.000Z","msg":"我跌崩咗隻門牙 有親戚係入面做唔洗排 <br />\n轉介上唔記得咗幾樓嘅港大牙科中心 有個靚女醫生幫我補 等咗三個幾月傷埋神經線  慳嗰幾千搞到要杜牙根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7581f3206be560a701f0e634908b561826236cd0","tid":636781,"uid":1403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T02:33:13.000Z","msg":"做左十一年教材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個去睇個牙醫姐姐成個波壓落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbcf92a91c6d789f4f7fcd7fb3fbd4c36f51053","tid":636781,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae3d4c67c631c28e7a555906bfbe66cdd78af620","tid":636781,"uid":24350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T01:48:24.000Z","msg":"仲要排既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係電話預約<br />\nBtw 樓主係想箍牙?<br />\n我之前有問過D姑娘話唔再收新症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申箍左五年就拆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:32:06.000Z","msg":"電話預約係14歲以下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccce754e018793ea2919ab407b281d48e87bde9","tid":636781,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T11:40:40.000Z","msg":"原來都幾多長期教材院友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我諗我個人應該貢獻過三五七份research articles<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望佢地acknowledgement 嗰度有提過下我"},{"pid":"8c356e76115e9c3587ea8dd071d28e5766468edc","tid":636781,"uid":137521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:18:04.000Z","msg":"d學生態度好好，跟進服務好細心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做手術日期好大彈性，可以假期先去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：細個去完醫好晒副牙俾個靚仔牙醫搞到自己都有d想做牙醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b318097823733e3713e1db8b02a31b58c822fe6c","tid":636781,"uid":10464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:32:56.000Z","msg":"我上個禮拜二先排完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係智慧齒<br />\n我自己係夜晚12點幾過去西營盤<br />\n跟住喺西營盤周圍fing 又係M記坐<br />\n因為我住喺新界垃圾地方 <br />\n就算搭頭班車都應該趕唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好似四點幾左右就走去排第一<br />\n然後就坐左係地下等 好眼瞓 又悶<br />\n之後應該接近五點就有一對情侶嚟咗<br />\n陸陸續續啲人開始嚟<br />\n好似到6點左右 朝頭早嘅籌就派晒 得8個<br />\n6點半 醫院就開放大堂入去畀你坐得舒服啲喺度等<br />\n之後姑娘喺度說明 又要等等等等到八點派籌<br />\n派完籌都咪咁開心住 仲係有排等<br />\n等登記都有排 登完記之後又等一排先見醫生 睇下收唔收你<br />\n即係我拎第一都要等咁耐 後過我嗰啲應該仲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢嗰度係話 <br />\n嗰日只係決定收唔收你 唔會喺嗰日治療你<br />\n不過可能我個case太緊急 <br />\n即日refer我去專科 失驚無神就做咗個放膿手術<br />\n痛撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到而家都仲痛緊<br />\n之後我仲要去排期去醫院剝牙 <br />\n好快 星期二又覆診啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d492328fb3ef4953a1ee012a9591031a8211e5","tid":636781,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"上次凌晨5點去<br />\n排第2個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後大約7,8點先滿"},{"pid":"a521d882a3d8a05049e8375d5296525b68aadccb","tid":636781,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:47:18.000Z","msg":"btw<br />\n上次我去剝智慧齒<br />\n每次剝1邊(2隻)<br />\n因為有隻生得太奇特<br />\n個學生手勢唔算好(講明先我唔係怪佢)<br />\n真係痛撚到仆街,打左麻醉都feel到痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後學生剝唔掂,要教授出手<br />\n嚇到我心肝仔都跳埋出黎<br />\n教授大大力咁扯,但都係剝唔到出黎<br />\n平時正常牙5分鐘剝完,我果隻搞左大約半個鐘先剝到<br />\n最後剝出黎發現有隻仆街牙有倒勾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後塊面腫左半個月先收腫,好傷好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過個傷口冇咩問題,埋口都幾靚<br />\n4隻剝哂塊面都尖左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240129840df31c3eca67db218af8cf63ae88687e","tid":636781,"uid":151534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1781b029d617decab300699c20dddf534aa4d56","tid":636781,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0090eac958de963c1be113472ff04aa8788bc156","tid":636781,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T08:53:03.000Z","msg":"唔係要睇下你有教學用途既咩?<br />\n利申:細個做過好多年教學工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T08:54:11.000Z","msg":"我打橫生智慧齒同生喺大牙後面夠唔夠教學價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T13:47:49.000Z","msg":"橫生一定收"}]}